CONTEXT CompositionISA_HeteroSubSuper IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT CompositionISA_HeteroSubSuper
{+ This test must succeed because meet(A,B) = A exists.
   A is a subtype of B, so they share concept A. +}

CLASSIFY A ISA B

RELATION r[W*A]
RELATION s[B*Z]
RELATION result[W*Z]

RULE testCompositionISA: result = r;s

ENDCONTEXT
